HEADWORD: Plugging
<hw>Plug"ging</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of stopping
with a plug.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The material of which a plug or stopple is
made.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Plum</ent>⟦br⟧
